363
00:17:16.505 --> 00:17:18.105
of environments from households

364
00:17:18.685 --> 00:17:20.345
and to those that are highly significant and

365
00:17:20.345 --> 00:17:23.345
or dangerous in feeding hospitals, infrastructure, projects,

366
00:17:23.345 --> 00:17:27.185
