00:20:04.075 --> 00:20:05.815
We are working on ways to streamline how

429
00:20:05.815 --> 00:20:07.535
to identify applicants who may qualify.

430
00:20:08.935 --> 00:20:10.725
There are no undue costs for registration.

431
00:20:11.125 --> 00:20:13.565
Electrical workers pay a registration fee once practicing

432
00:20:13.565 --> 00:20:15.205
license fees are flat fees regardless

433
